    <p>MANDORA SAVES CHRIST­MAS Thun­der­cats Roar Watch it at: Car­toon Net­work (StarHub TV Chan­nel 316 and Sing­tel TV Chan­nel 226) on Dec 20, 1.30pm</p>
    <p>Thun­der­cats, a pop­u­lar 1980s car­toon se­ries that chron­i­cles the ad­ven­tures of a cat-hu­man hy­brid alien species, was re­booted early this year.</p>
    <p>While the new car­toon, Thun­der­cats Roar, takes a more hu­mor­ous slant, it fea­tures the same char­ac­ters that made the fran­chise so pop­u­lar: a group of heroic Thun­der­cats led by Lion-O who goes up against vil­lains led by Mumm-Ra.</p>
    <p>The fi­nal episode of the se­ries is a Christ­mas­themed spe­cial in which the Thun­der­cats try to help Santa Claus.</p>

